node.text:
It’s just the beginning ✌🏽

Our Chief Communications Officer Damon Jones and 8:46 filmmaker @camrusj talked about why it’s important to reclaim the time stolen from Black communities with stories of love, hope and even humor! 

The #846Films debut September 4th at 8pmET on @CBS. Click #linkinbio to get the story behind 8:46 Films. 

#846Films #WidenTheScreen
This film series is one of the best things @proctergamble has ever done. Thank you for lifting voices up, and smart move getting @camrusj because he’s the GOAT
